title: PhiZone Privilege Escalation Test
description: In order to access all features that PhiZone provides, you must first take this test so as to unlock them. There are 15 objective questions and 3 subjective questions. Plus, you'll also need to provide us with a chart you've made so that we can truly assess your proficiency.
chart_question: Please enter a valid link to an autoplay of your chart. You may explain in detail about some parts of the chart if necessary.
